				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Mitcheypoo’s Guide to Pulling Well<a name="71705"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 1 05 12:15 AM</span></td>
