				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Mitcheypoo’s Guide to Pulling Well<a name="71736"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 2 05 3:07 PM</span></td>
